column1: Free and Open Source Software Developers European Meeting
column7:
FOSDEM is a free event for software developers to meet, share ideas and collaborate.

Every year, thousands of developers of free and open source software from all over the world gather at the event in Brussels.
An Open-IT fair that also runs Open Awards

column1: GNOME Users And Developers European Conference
Free and Open Source Software Auditing
column7: The next EU-FOSSA 2 Hackathon, on 4/5th May, has broadened its scope. It will still have a large focus on Apache Tomcat, but will now also include other communities under the Apache Software Foundation (ASF). Aditionally, the Hackathon will be offering training sessions on some of the latest ASF projects.

Die Konferenz: In 24 Stunden wird auf drei Bühnen in der großartigen Volksbühne Berlin und im Anschluss im Mensch Meier ein Rundumschlag über alle relevanten aktuellen Debatten der digitalen Welt stattfinden.
